{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I said, it was Aunt Paula who was-- I, I remember there was-- in those days, perhaps even parents did not believe in really shedding, in really giving children all kinds of hugs and kisses and love and, and saying, repeating that I love you or whatever.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- I, I was treated by my aunts very well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But of course, I-- since I was a very independent child, they would also look over my shoulders and not permit me to play with older children where I was really interested in sexual adventures-- I mean, you know, to get books.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember we had a little library, and so I took out a book on sex.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And God forbid, it was forbidden, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was at the time already 12, 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would have to read it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember at night look through all the pictures.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would go into huddles later on during the day with other friends and say, did you hear-- do you know about this?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you know about that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was just-- it was just passe, you know-- a penis or, God forbid, anybody would say that word or a vagina or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- or, you know, we would go into huddles how children are born or, you know, what happens when you get married and so on, so forth.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one ever told us anything about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember one day, I read the book at night with a flashlight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I put it under the bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the morning, I got up and went to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
